        { slug "scheduling-every-minute-revisited" </ url derived /> date @2016-02-08T16:08:20@ updated @2016-02-08T16:08:20@ excerpt <"Late last year, I published an article entitled \"How I Plan Every Minute of My Day to Stay Productive,\" where I described my personal daily workflow of planning the tasks that I need to accomplish and then adjusting that plan as necessary throughout the day. I have a new job now, so I want to post an update on how well the approach is working in a new environment with new responsibilities, and how I've made a few tweaks to the process."> order 11 }
