        { slug "master-foo-and-the-technical-recruiter" </ url derived /> date @2015-05-28T19:19:12@ updated @2015-05-28T19:19:12@ excerpt "I found Eric Raymond's Unix Koans of Master Foo several years ago and simply loved them. Like the Zen koans they are taken from, they are a succinct way to communicate concepts of software development, specifically as they relate to the Unix development subculture." order 16 }
